CCM Investment Advisers, LLC is a registered investment adviser with over $2.2 billion in discretionary assets under management.  We offer a complete array of investment styles with proven records of competitive investment returns.  CCM was founded on the philosophy of structuring a quality investment advisory firm that provides individual attention to the investment objectives of each client. CCM's structure is designed to attract and retain both experienced investment managers and highly rated business school graduates.


