CCM Investment Advisers is a privately owned investment counseling firm located in Columbia, South Carolina. CCM provides asset management services for individuals, corporations, municipalities and institutions.


ABOUT CCM INVESTMENT ADVISERS


CCM's only business is the active management of investment portfolios. Our clients include endowments, foundations, pension and profit sharing plans, insurance companies, trusts and individuals. CCM has over $2.2 billion in discretionary client assets under management.  CCM was founded on the philosophy of structuring a quality investment advisory firm that provides individual attention to the investment objectives of each client. CCM's structure is designed to attract and retain both experienced investment managers and highly rated business school graduates.







Through shared ownership in the profitability of the firm, CCM Investment Advisers' investment professionals have a clear vested interest in the long term success of our clients. CCM's portfolio managers understand each client's investment objectives. This permits the portfolio manager to integrate our disciplined, conservative approach with an appreciation of each client's individual circumstances.


